Great British Menu - Series 10, Episodes 16 to 20




Northern Ireland

Three of Northern Ireland's top chefs - Chris McGowan, Danni Barry and Ben Arnold - go head to head with their courses to impress the judges. Former champion Chris is back for glory and determined to reach the banquet, but he's up against two newcomers with their sights firmly set on victory.




Original Air Dates: 31-Aug-2015 to 04-Sep-2015
